#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux debian-buster debian-unstable mageia-cauldron
msgid ""
"An overlay filesystem combines two filesystems - an B<upper> filesystem and "
"a B<lower> filesystem.  When a name exists in both filesystems, the object "
"in the upper filesystem is visible while the object in the lower filesystem "
"is either hidden or, in the case of directories, merged with the upper "
"object."
